Name: SecondaryMatchedReport
SqlScript: SELECT d.dwh_id as dwhId, LiveRowId, d.pkv, d.ccc_number as cccNumber, d.patient_pk as PatientPK, d.FacilityCode, d.matched_pkv as MatchedPkv, d.matched_ccc_number as matchedCCCNumber, d.matched_nupi as matchedNupi, site_codes as OtherSiteCodes FROM [dbo].[secondary_matched_output] d

Name: ValidationReport
SqlScript: SELECT d.dwh_id as dwhId, LiveRowId, d.golden_id as GoldenId, d.pkv, d.ccc_number as cccNumber, d.patient_pk as PatientPK, d.FacilityCode, d.docket as Docket, d.nupi as Nupi, d.ccc_numbers as OtherCCCNumber, site_codes as OtherSiteCodes FROM [dbo].[validation_report] d

Name: Predictions
SqlScript: SELECT code, Name, id, PatientPID, PatientCccNumber, Gender, DOB, LiveRowId, risk_score, FacilityCode, Description, RiskFactors, EvaluationDate, DateCreated FROM   PatientPrediction

Name: DuplicateReport
SqlScript: SELECT d.dwh_id as dwhId, LiveRowId, d.golden_id as GoldenId, d.record_count as RecordCount, d.pkv, d.gender, d.dob, d.docket, d.nupi, d.ccc_number as cccNumber, d.patient_pk as PatientPK, d.FacilityCode, other_site_codes as OtherSiteCodes FROM [dbo].[deduplication_report] d

Name: DataExchange
SqlScript: Select FacilityCode, FacilityName, County, period, indicator_name, indicator_value from Indicator
